#Car rental service

Client selects car from list. Client fills reservation form pointing rental period. 
Client pays the bill. Administrator registers return of car. 
If car is damaged, administrator bill for damage. 
Administrator can reject reservation pointing rejection reason

##Used technologies

* Java SE8, Java EE (Servlets, JSP, JSTL)
* MySQL, JDBC, Apache Commons DBCP
* Apache Tomcat 9
* JUnit 4, Hamcrest, Mockito, Powermock
* Cloudinary
* CSS, Bootstrap
* Apache Maven, Git, Apache Log4j 2

Schema creation script can be found under *resources/db* folder